## Vibe Coding Guardrails

- No duplicate abstractions — check before creating.
- No silent refactors — stay in scope.
- Flag tech debt without fixing it.
- Checkpoint after 5 significant changes.

## Windsurf-Specific Notes

- Use Cascade flows for multi-step tasks with clear step descriptions.
- Keep individual Cascade steps small and reversible.
- Use inline comments to mark changes made during a session.
- Prefer targeted file edits over full file rewrites.
